iscussion", "Increase the employee''s compensation"], "question": "An employee has been consistently exceeding their targets and delivering high-quality work. However, they are reluctant to take on additional responsibilities. What is the BEST way for the manager to address this issue and foster a greater sense of accountability?", "skill_tag": "Accountability and career growth", "difficulty": "hard", "correct_answer": "Schedule a career development discussion", "estimated_time": 115}, {"id": 14, "type": "mcq", "options": ["Implement a system of peer-to-peer feedback", "Restructure the team''s goals and responsibilities", "Provide additional resources and training to the team", "Increase the frequency of one-on-one meetings"], "question": "A team is struggling to meet their quarterly goals, and the manager suspects a lack of individual accountability as the root cause. What is the BEST way for the manager to address this issue and improve the team''s performance?", "skill_tag": "Accountability and team dynamics", "difficulty": "hard", "correct_answer": "Implement a system of peer-to-peer feedback", "estimated_time": 110}, {"id": 15, "type": "mcq", "options": ["Provide additional training and support for the changes", "Mandate the changes and enforce compliance", "Offer incentives for adopting the new policy", "Involve employees in the decision-making process"], "question": "A new company policy has been implemented, but some employees are reluctant to adopt the changes. What is the BEST way for a manager to ensure accountability and buy-in from the team?", "skill_tag": "Accountability and change management", "difficulty": "hard", "correct_answer": "Involve employees in the decision-making process", "estimated_time": 120}]', '[{"is_correct": false, "time_taken": 0, "question_id": 1, "selected_answer": "Responsibility"}, {"is_correct": null, "time_taken": 0, "question_id": 2, "selected_answer": null}, {"is_correct": null, "time_taken": 0, "question_id": 3, "selected_a